## 7. Entity Summary & Suggested DB Tables

| Table | Key Fields |
|---|---|
| `topics` | `id`, `slug`, `name`, `tags[]`, `platform`, `signal_count`, `unanswered_signals`, `urgency_score`, `avg_response_time_hours`, `top_platform`, `last_scraped_at`, `next_refresh_at`, `status` |
| `subtopics` | `id`, `parent_topic_id`, `name`, `signal_count` |
| `creators` | `id`, `username`, `display_name`, `avatar_url`, `bio`, `is_verified`, `follower_count`, `follower_growth_7d_pct`, `post_count`, `transcribed_count`, `avg_urgency_score`, `incumbency_score`, `total_signals_generated` |
| `posts` | `id`, `creator_id`, `topic_id`, `title`, `caption`, `excerpt`, `hashtags[]`, `content_type` (enum: reel/video/image), `thumbnail_url`, `video_url`, `external_url`, `platform`, `published_at`, `view_count`, `like_count`, `comment_count`, `duration_seconds`, `engagement_rate`, `urgency_score`, `analyzed_signal_count`, `high_urgency_signal_count`, `signal_velocity_pct_change`, `last_scraped_at`, `next_refresh_at`, `ai_summary` |
| `transcripts` | `id`, `post_id`, `segments` (JSONB: `[{start_time, text}]`) |
| `signals` | `id`, `post_id`, `topic_id`, `creator_id`, `text`, `urgency_score`, `status` (enum: unanswered/answered/claimed), `claimed_by`, `platform`, `thread_name`, `created_at` |
| `signal_velocity` | `id`, `post_id`, `recorded_at`, `count_per_hour` |
| `popular_queries` | `id`, `topic_id`, `query_text`, `rate_per_hour`, `recorded_at` |
| `rising_queries` | `id`, `topic_id`, `query_text`, `growth_pct`, `is_breakout`, `recorded_at` |
| `monthly_stats` | `id`, `topic_id`, `year`, `month`, `answered_count`, `unanswered_count` |
| `news_items` | `id`, `topic_id`, `headline`, `source`, `thumbnail_url`, `published_at`, `external_url` |
| `users` | `id`, `email`, `display_name`, `avatar_url`, `role` |
| `market_ticks` | `id`, `ticker_symbol`, `price`, `change_pct`, `recorded_at` |
